'''EoLA''' (from ''Esperanto — Lingvo Arta'' "Esperanto — Art Language") is an international festival of [[Esperanto]] arts and literature sponsored by the [[Russian Esperantist Union]] and the [[Russian Esperantist Youth Movement]]. The festival began in 1998 in [[Volgograd]], the latest one was in 2005 in [[Jekaterinburg]].

