sh Bhagwani | Nirmal Bhagwani |Website : [http://Www.sindhibandhu.com www.sindhibandhu.com] |- | ''Sindhu Halchal'' ({{lang-sd|سِنڌُو هلِچلِ}}) | Daily/weekly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[Damoh]] ([[Madhya Pradesh|MP]]) | Sajay Rohra | | |- | ''Sanwad Sindhi'' ({{lang-sd|سنودِ سنڌِي}}) | Daily/weekly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[New Delhi]] | Shrikant Bhatia ([[Bhatia (caste)|Bhatia]]) | | |- | ''Sindhi Gulistan'' ({{lang-sd|سنڌِي گُلِستان}}) | Daily/weekly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[New Delhi]] | Anjali Tulsiani | | |- | ''Sindhu Parag'' ({{lang-sd|سنڌِوُ پرآڳ}}) | Monthly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[Rewa, Madhya Pradesh|Rewa]] ([[Madhya Pradesh|MP]]) | Shri Vijay Thawani | | |- | ''Sindhudee'' ({{lang-sd|سنڌِوُدي}}) | Monthly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[Nagpur]] | Shri Tulsi Setiya | Shri Kishore Lalwani | |- | ''Sindhi Sadabahar'' ({{lang-sd|سِنڌِي سدابهار}}) | Monthly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[Rajkot]] | Shri Jayant Dhanrajani | Shri Dhirwani Umesh | |- | ''Dile Sindh'' ({{lang-sd|دِلِ سِنڌ}}) | Fortnightly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[Delhi]] | Shri Mahesh Chhabaria | | |- | ''Aman-e-Hind'' ({{lang-sd|امنِ هندِ}}) | Monthly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[Bhopal]] ([[Madhya Pradesh|MP]]) | SShri Dev Jhurani | | |- | ''Sindh Panchayat Samachar'' ({{lang-sd|سِنڌِي پنچائيِت سماچار}}) | Fortnightly (Akhbar Hindi - Ziban Sindhi) | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[Neemach]] ([[Madhya Pradesh|MP]]) | Shri Kamal Vardhani | | Padho ain Padhayo - Sindhyat Ji Jyot Jagayo پڙهو ۽ پڙهائِيو،سِنڌُ جيِ جِيُوتِ جلائِيو |- | ''Sabh Jo Bhalo'' ({{lang-sd|سڀ جو ڀلو}}) | Monthly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[Katni]] ([[Madhya Pradesh|MP]]) | Shri Ghanshyam Bellani | | |- | ''Sindhu Awaj'' ({{lang-sd|سِنڌُو اَوجَ}}) | Quarterly | [[Sindhi language|Sindhi]] | [[Faizabad]] ([[Uttar Pradesh|UP]]) | Shri Omprakash Omi | | |}
